# Part 2

## Describe an interesting video.

An interesting video I watched recently was a documentary about artificial intelligence and humanoid robots. I watched it about a month ago in my dorm room on YouTube after finishing my homework.

The video explained how AI systems are trained and how robots can interact with humans in daily life. What impressed me most was that some robots could recognize emotions and even hold simple conversations. Since I’m a computer science student and I’m really interested in AI, I found the topic extremely engaging.

I watched it mainly because I enjoy technology-related content, especially videos connected to the future of AI. Besides, many people online were discussing it at that time, so I became curious.

After watching it, I felt both excited and inspired. It made me realize how quickly technology is developing, and it also motivated me to study harder and learn more about artificial intelligence in the future.

---

### 中文翻译：

我最近看过一个很有趣的视频，是关于人工智能和人形机器人的纪录片。我大概一个月前在宿舍里做完作业后，通过YouTube观看的。

这个视频讲述了AI系统是如何训练的，以及机器人如何在日常生活中与人类互动。最让我印象深刻的是，有些机器人甚至能够识别人类情绪，并进行简单对话。因为我是计算机专业学生，而且对人工智能特别感兴趣，所以我觉得这个主题非常吸引人。

我之所以会看这个视频，主要是因为我平时很喜欢科技相关内容，尤其是关于AI未来发展的内容。另外，当时网上很多人都在讨论它，所以我很好奇。

看完之后，我既兴奋又受到激励。它让我意识到科技发展的速度非常快，也让我更有动力继续学习人工智能。

